The #StarBaby Album is OUT!  I chose this cover cause this picture represents a time where I was hungry and determined to make this music/rap work for me. I was grimy and I wasn’t settling for nothing less than the goals I had in mind. This picture also represents a time in music where my sound and the sound that I loved to hear was a certain way and this album embodies that sound perfectly. My goal is to help bring that authentic Texas sound back to the forefront of the entire rap game while also giving the world some songs to ride to forever! I put some of my favorite Texas legends and producers on this album and i can’t wait for y’all to hear it! #StarBaby ⭐️👶🏾

Fly High Pops 🕊️ Love You 4ever ♥️
I witnessed you be a stand up guy my entire life. I saw you work & provide for your family my entire life. I saw you take care & love my mama unconditionally my entire life. I saw you take care of every last one of your kids & many more my entire life. You went Above & Beyond being a great father and I can’t thank you enough for the image/example you have left me with as a man. You poured into everyone that knew you and now your spirit & mentality is with us all. You persevered through many tough situations in life and I’m very proud of you. From me (your youngest) and all my siblings, your grandkids, nieces & nephews, and my mama.. we love you, we miss u 😢 (11/26/49 - 7/24/23) 🕊️

P.S. This song will forever remind me of all the times I rode to work with you at night as a kid. This is your favorite song, and one of mines too
Laid to Rest, Properly.. Rest in Peace Pops 🕊️ We Love You, We Miss You. Hardest day of my life 😢

Just how you wanted it pops, simple & private w/ close family & friends. Your kids and grandkids did your Eulogy, Your wife (Mama) was strong, held you down & spoke amazing words during the hardest time of her life. We buried you with your pops (Grandpa) just like you asked. It was beautiful. Fly High, Love You, & Goodbye for now. 🕊️🕊️🕊️

🎥: @swag214
